paragraphs:
This 2 in 1 USB Dongle  can be used for WiFi and Bluetooth.
Both WiFi and Bluetooth function can be used simultaneously.

A nano-sized USB Wi-Fi adapter with Bluetooth 4.0 that supports Wi-Fi up to 150Mbps while allowing users to connect to all the latest Bluetooth devices such as mobile phones, tablets, mice, keyboards, printers and more.
